{"tid":1992481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨議員 許智勇或者鄺神入唔入嚟唔該","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T08:10:29.000Z","uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f06c3ba66cfe6a21d3819f9d19f624517c0498d","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=information/category&amp;cid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dinformation%2Fcategory%26cid%3D2&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=4bb9f805\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=information/category&amp;cid=2</a><br />\n<br />\n關於民主黨<br />\n基本信念<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.香港是中國不可分割的一部分，我們支持香港回歸中國。</span><br />\n <br />\n2.回歸後實行一國兩制、高度自治及港人民主治港，符合香港人意願，有利於穩定與繁榮，對中國的發展起促進作用。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.我們關心中國，作為中國人民的一分子，香港人有權利及責任去參與及評議國家事務。</span><br />\n <br />\n4.對中國政府任何涉及或影響香港的政策，我們都會反映港人意見，爭取港人的利益得到合理的照顧。<br />\n <br />\n5.民主是實現高度自治的必要條件，是殖民地統治結束後理所當然的發展。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想做分化撚<br />\n但係我真係諗唔明究竟你地點樣一路嗌 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n一路話自己係民主黨立法會議員<br />\n其實立法會選舉都近啦<br />\n民主黨有無咩回應<br />\n你點光復香港?直接支持回歸?<br />\n<br />\n如果大家屌我係分化撚<br />\n咁我只會話民主黨嘅信念同我嘅信念根本係相反<br />\n我唔知大家嘅信念係咩啦"},{"pid":"2e8859bcb2063fb4bc5177612634f8d551c75da4","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4282d03bbe255b7e1c909b028d8bb7b40f1b5e36","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadfb59649178e43621c68f9fcef1f0306845a8b","tid":1992481,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b033e0d242e36185072187112885825db25bcf70","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3902f7099b52ce0e9980d04e798a9f92779c5d","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19b447661e7881b81f871baca1f0fc050b13729","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45b17b6e0536dc651a11146bee828594e27a31cc","tid":1992481,"uid":113185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f06c3ba66cfe6a21d3819f9d19f624517c0498d","tid":1992481,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=information/category&amp;cid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dinformation%2Fcategory%26cid%3D2&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=4bb9f805\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=information/category&amp;cid=2</a><br />\n<br />\n關於民主黨<br />\n基本信念<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.香港是中國不可分割的一部分，我們支持香港回歸中國。</span><br />\n <br />\n2.回歸後實行一國兩制、高度自治及港人民主治港，符合香港人意願，有利於穩定與繁榮，對中國的發展起促進作用。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.我們關心中國，作為中國人民的一分子，香港人有權利及責任去參與及評議國家事務。</span><br />\n <br />\n4.對中國政府任何涉及或影響香港的政策，我們都會反映港人意見，爭取港人的利益得到合理的照顧。<br />\n <br />\n5.民主是實現高度自治的必要條件，是殖民地統治結束後理所當然的發展。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想做分化撚<br />\n但係我真係諗唔明究竟你地點樣一路嗌 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n一路話自己係民主黨立法會議員<br />\n其實立法會選舉都近啦<br />\n民主黨有無咩回應<br />\n你點光復香港?直接支持回歸?<br />\n<br />\n如果大家屌我係分化撚<br />\n咁我只會話民主黨嘅信念同我嘅信念根本係相反<br />\n我唔知大家嘅信念係咩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:4